OL,4,Cpedestrian with patrol car
OL,6,FA police officer has been cleared of
OL,7,Fkilling a pedestrian with his patrol
OL,8,Fcar after charges were dropped.
OL,10,FPc Christopher Corker, 40, was alleged
OL,11,Fto have knocked down and killed 27-
OL,12,Fyear-old Arthur Holscher-Ermert in a
OL,13,Froad in Peacehaven, East Sussex.
OL,15,FMr Holscher-Ermert was struck by the
OL,16,Fvehicle just after 11.10pm on April 30
OL,17,F2022, and was confirmed dead at the
OL,18,Fscene.
