OL,4,Cpedestrian with patrol car
OL,6,FCorker, of Shandon Road, Worthing,
OL,7,FWest Sussex, had pleaded not guilty to
OL,8,Fcausing death by dangerous driving and
OL,9,Fcausing death by careless or
OL,10,Finconsiderate driving.
OL,12,FOn Monday, the Sussex Police officer,
OL,13,Fwho was on unconditional bail,
OL,14,Fattended the Old Bailey for what had
OL,15,Fbeen scheduled to be the first day of
OL,16,Fhis trial.
