OL,6,FHowever, prosecutor Jonathan Sandiford
OL,7,FKC offered no evidence at a hearing
OL,8,Fbefore Judge Richard Marks KC, saying
OL,9,Fthat in light of expert reports there
OL,10,Fwas no longer a realistic prospect of
OL,11,Fa conviction.
OL,13,FJudge Marks formally entered not
OL,14,Fguilty verdicts and offered his
OL,15,Fcondolences to the family, saying: "It
OL,16,Fappears to have been a tragic
OL,17,Faccident."
