OL,6,FIn a statement after the hearing, the
OL,7,Ffamily said: "Instead of attending
OL,8,Ftrial today, we as a family have had
OL,9,Fto process the sudden news that the
OL,10,FCPS are discontinuing criminal
OL,11,Fproceedings against Pc Corker.
OL,13,F"This is incredibly upsetting and
OL,14,Fdisappointing; it has been over two
OL,15,Fyears since Arthur died.
OL,17,F"We were hoping to start to get
OL,18,Fanswers about what happened to Arthur
OL,19,Fand why on April 30, 2022.
